  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink291-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirintu mīḷkiṉṟa talaimakaṉ colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the hero, having fixed the time for marriage and parted, and then returning, said.                  
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink291">
<l>mayilka ḷālak kuṭiñai yiraṭṭun</l>
<l>tuṟukal laṭukkat tatuvē paṇaittō</l>
<l>ḷāytaḻai nuṭaṅku malkuṟ</l>
<l>kātali yuṟaiyu naṉinal lūrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The very good village,</l>
        <l>where our lover—</l>
        <l>she of bamboo shoulders</l>
        <l>and hips on which choice foliage sways—dwells,</l>
        <l>belongs to the mountain slope</l>
        <l>of thick rocks,</l>
        <l>where the owls hoot in alternation</l>
        <l>as the peacocks cry.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
